Since this extension is not yet on the Chrome Store, here are the instructions to test it.

Download all the files into another file on your computer. 
Then go into Chrome and type this chrome://extensions/
In the top right corner activate the developping mode
In top left corner click on "load an unpacked extension" and load the file containing the extension
Activate the extension, pin it and then go to another tab, any website and test it. 
